title: American Peach Cobbler
ingredients: ['8 fresh peaches, peeled, pitted and sliced', '110g butter, cut into pieces', '110g dark brown soft sugar', '250g plain flour', '400g caster sugar', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 eggs, lightly beaten', '250ml vegetable oil', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon']
